high_descs: Move forward then turn right walk straight toward the fridge then turn right head to the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Turn right then walk forward then turn left facing the trash bin
Slice the apple in the bin
Drop the knife in the bin
Pick up the slice apple in the bin
Turn left head to the microwave on your left
Open the microwave put in the slice apple, take it out then close the microwave
Turn left move forward turn left face the trash bin
Put the heated slice apple in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice apple in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn right and walk toward the fridge, then turn right into the kitchen and approach the sink
Pick up the butter knife from the sink
Turn right and walk around the end of the counter to the black trash bin
Cut the green apple in the bin with the knife
Put the knife in the trash bin
Pick up an apple piece from the trash bin
Turn left and walk back into the kitchen then turn left to face the microwave above the oven
Heat the apple piece in the microwave then remove it
Turn left and walk back around to the trash bin
Put the apple piece in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple piece in the trash bin

high_descs: Walk 1 step to the front, turn right, walk straight, turn right near the fridge and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife near the fork in the sink.
Walk to your right, turn right near the fridge and turn right to go to the black trash can.
Cut the apple in the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Pick up a slice of apple from the trash can.
Walk to your left, turn right near the fridge, walk straight, turn right to go to the stove and look up to the microwave on top of the stove.
Open the microwave, put the slice of apple in, heat it for a few seconds, pick it up again and close the microwave
Go back to the black trash can near the fridge.
Put the slice of apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of apple in the trash can near the fridge.
